%header
    %h1 Yesod Book: $title$
%article
    #status Chapter status: $show.chapterStatus.chapter$
    %p
        %b NOTE: $
        The content for the book has not yet been updated for Yesod version 0.7. This is a top priority and will be done shortly. Look for a blog post when the transition is complete.
    ^html^
    %p
        %a!href=@BookR@ Table of Contents
        $maybe previous p
            %br
            %a!href=@ChapterR.unpack.chapterSlug.p@
                Previous: $chapterTitle.p$
            %span.status $chapterStatus.p$
        $maybe next p
            %br
            %a!href=@ChapterR.unpack.chapterSlug.p@
                Next: $chapterTitle.p$
            %span.status $chapterStatus.p$
